Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:59.28,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,were drawn to my heart's desire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.95,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k27}o{\k29}mo{\k36}u {\k28}ma{\k42}ma {\k16}ka{\k23}ki {\k31}su{\k31}be{\k60}rase{\k30}te
