Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.40,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k28}ha{\k35}ne {\k34}wo {\k23}te{\k43}ni {\k24}i{\k23}re{\k62}te
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.40,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,with which I could fly freely.
