Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.95,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k28}so{\k19}ra {\k18}no {\k51}mu{\k24}ko{\k23}u {\k21}he {\k16}i{\k31}ki{\k22}ta{\k43}i {\k66}na
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.95,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,which my pure eyes desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.12,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k18}ko{\k27}re {\k23}to{\k23}na{\k39}i {\k28}ne{\k22}ga{\k17}i {\k51}ka{\k69}ra
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.12,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,If one wish could be granted
